            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-03-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-03-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="22" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d22">
                <head>No. 22.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Braida</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-03-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 28,
                            1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>You are not authorized to perform diplomatic functions, and will not meddle
                        in political affairs in Mosquito. Naval vessel will soon reach
                        Bluefields.</p>
            </div>
